<emphasis id="597AEFE0D4AA6AD4BB452897392EB6A6" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="67">A</emphasis>
habit and mature flower 
<emphasis id="1033D63A2E8EA137D4E66FA0C618E721" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="67">B</emphasis>
habit and developing fruit 
<emphasis id="7F30E8F1D74696984BAE4DD4E1E98658" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="67">C</emphasis>
developing flowers on hooked inflorescence 
